{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Ecosystem_Builder.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>Wild City takes inspiration from &quot;Slay the Spire&quot; and &quot;Dorfromantik&quot; to create a unique strategic roguelike experience where deckbuilding and tile placement meet.<br>Each card represents a unique animal, plant, or insect!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Placement.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>Cards are tiles that the player will place on the grid. <br>Each card makes money when placed, your final objective will be to make a lot of money and make Wild City prosper.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Deckbuilder.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>Build a deck out of hundreds of different cards, choose wisely as you look for the best synergies, as for every card there are many different possible interactions.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Cards.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>Keep playing to unlock new cards and discover all different kinds of ecosystems.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Combos.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>Each card will interact with the others on the board uniquely. Try to trigger crazy chain reactions through strategic placements!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/extras/Chain.gif?t=1715332222\" /><br><br>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1715332222","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436970/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1715332222",